data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 244 Foxglove Drive! Nestled in a peaceful country neighborhood of Bloomfield Acres, this contemporary 2-story house offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and ample parking space for several vehicles or your RV, this property is designed to meet all your needs.  Step inside and to the right to be greeted by a spacious office space, ideal for those who work from home or need a quiet area to focus. The main floor boasts  hardwood floors that add warmth and charm to this open concept  living space.   Cozy up next to the gas fireplace on chilly nights or relax on the large deck with a 12x16 Pergola and swing. Imagine sipping your morning coffee in the privacy of the screened gazebo while enjoying the beauty of nature in this private backyard.  The fenced yard provides a safe haven for children and pets to play freely. Need extra storage or a workshop? Look no further than the 24 x 28 pole barn, complete with electric, heating and air conditioning.  Other notable features include a Rinnai tankless water heater, reverse osmosis system, electronic air scrubber, and a convenient 50 amp RV hookup. The property sits on .50 acres and is situated on a tranquil cul-de-sac.  With its side entry 2-car garage and practical layout, this home checks all the boxes for both functionality and aesthetics.   Motivated Sellers bring all offers!
